Key Match Events: Niclas Füllkrug scored the opening goal for Germany at the 27th minute, assisted by Jamal Musiala. Jamal Musiala doubled Germany's lead at the 58th minute with a goal from one on one, assisted by Florian Wirtz. Florian Wirtz scored the third goal for Germany at the 66th minute, assisted by Jamal Musiala. Aleksandar Pavlović scored the fourth goal for Germany at the 77th minute. Kai Havertz scored a penalty at the 81st minute to complete Germany's 5-0 victory.
Post-Match Reflections: Julian Nagelsmann's side secured a comfortable win in their Nations League campaign opener.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Niclas Fullkrug scored his first Germany goal since joining West Ham in the summer.
